Transport Minister Fikile Mbalula will be scrapping taxis today. It's part of the revised Taxi Recapitalisation Programme. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Transport Minister Fikile Mbalula will be scrapping taxis on Friday. It's part of the revised Taxi Recapitalisation Programme. READ: Mbalula has grand plan for transport Since 2005, over 72 000 old and unsafe taxis have been removed from the roads. Over R400-million has been allocated in the transport ministry.